# Pulumi workspace local artifacts — never commit state, secrets, or installed deps.
/bin/
node_modules/
# Pulumi self-managed state lives in S3, but guard against an accidental local backend:
.pulumi/
# Stack configs (Pulumi.<stack>.yaml) ARE committed — they hold only non-secret
# config + the encryptionsalt; true secrets are `pulumi config set --secret`
# (encrypted with the stack's secrets provider) or live in SSM, never plaintext here.
